35
00:03:30,125 --> 00:03:31,708
Tsubaki!

36
00:03:32,791 --> 00:03:35,791
At least I had the chance
to see them all off...

37
00:03:35,875 --> 00:03:37,791
...with my own eyes,
on the outside.

38
00:03:37,875 --> 00:03:39,916
So I'm glad.

39
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:50,208
The pilots' brain waves
have crossed over.

40
00:03:50,291 --> 00:03:52,291
They're showing up
as theta waves.

41
00:03:52,375 --> 00:03:54,208
Although they're
about to go into battle,

42
00:03:54,291 --> 00:03:55,791
everyone's
completely relaxed.

43
00:03:55,875 --> 00:03:57,166
They're preserving their energy

44
00:03:57,250 --> 00:03:59,291
in preparation for
the big fight.

45
00:03:59,375 --> 00:04:01,041
Before we could
even bat an eye,

46
00:04:01,125 --> 00:04:04,208
those little brats
turned into real adults.

47
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,833
Where are Kazuki and others now?

48
00:04:09,916 --> 00:04:11,333
They traveled
outside the island's

49
