make it to the outer atmosphere
is thirty-seven percent.

221
00:11:21,583 --> 00:11:23,833
That means more than
one-third of them will make it

222
00:11:23,916 --> 00:11:27,000
to the enemy core that forms
the network in the sky.

223
00:11:27,083 --> 00:11:29,333
That is truly wonderful.

224
00:11:29,416 --> 00:11:31,291
I've been waiting
eagerly for this

225
00:11:31,375 --> 00:11:33,708
for more than thirty years.

226
00:11:34,083 --> 00:11:38,250
To the human race!
Victory shall be ours!

227
00:11:39,125 --> 00:11:41,583
And to the mastermind
behind Heaven's Door.

228
00:11:41,666 --> 00:11:43,666
May the fire from the
battles burn bright

229
00:11:43,750 --> 00:11:46,208
enough to reach your
soul Dr. Mitsuhiro.

230
00:11:46,291 --> 00:11:49,250
And may your
spirit rest in peace.

231
00:11:51,791 --> 00:11:55,500
There.
It's the North Pole.

232
00:11:57,375 --> 00:11:58,708
There they are!

233
00:11:58,791 --> 00:12:01,291
We'll need cover from all sides.
Let's go get 'em, boys.

234
00:12:20,916 --> 00:12:22,791
We'll drop the containers
in five seconds.

235
00:12:22,875 --> 00:12:26,416
Kazuki, Maya, Kenji, Canon.

236
00:12:26,500 --> 00:12:29,375
Come back alive.
And that is an order!

237
00:12:35,166 --> 00:12:36,750
Verifying landing point!

238
00:12:36,833 --> 00:12:38,833
I'm counting on you, Kenji.

239
00:12:43,125 --> 00:12:45,000
Point A is all clear.

240
00:12:45,083 --> 00:12:46,000
Here we go!

241
00:12:46,083 --> 00:12:47,666
--Roger that!
--Roger that!

242
00:12:57,166 --> 00:12:59,041
Here they come!

243
00:13:07,125 --> 00:13:09,041
Kazuki! Kenji and
I will create a barrier,

244
00:13:09,125 --> 00:13:09,916
then you break through.

245
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:10,791
Are you ready Kenji?

246
00:13:10,875 --> 00:13:12,333
You bet!

247
00:13:42,708 --> 00:13:44,458
Nice shot there Missy!

