00:13:45,916 --> 00:13:48,125
the one needing
rescuing from you now?

250
00:14:04,708 --> 00:14:09,208
Child of Alvis...
teach us the way to fight you.

251
00:14:12,541 --> 00:14:13,875
Prepare yourself.

252
00:14:13,958 --> 00:14:17,875
For you are now going to
destroy the humans of this land.

253
00:14:18,875 --> 00:14:22,541
No...
K-Kazuki...

254
00:14:34,125 --> 00:14:35,750
It'll be awhile
before the core's

255
00:14:35,833 --> 00:14:38,041
re-synchronization
will be ready.

256
00:14:38,125 --> 00:14:40,041
All right, then take
this time to prepare

257
00:14:40,125 --> 00:14:43,041
Tsubaki Minashiro
for the operation.

258
00:14:43,125 --> 00:14:44,666
It's times like these...

259
00:14:44,750 --> 00:14:46,250
...I wish Ayano
were still here.

260
00:14:46,333 --> 00:14:47,666
I'd imagine the battle at the

261
00:14:47,750 --> 00:14:50,125
North Pole's already begun,
wouldn't you agree?

262
00:14:50,208 --> 00:14:51,166
Yeah.

263
00:14:51,250 --> 00:14:53,166
It sure is hard not
having any clue

264
00:14:53,250 --> 00:14:55,875
how they're all doing
out there, huh?

265
00:14:55,958 --> 00:14:57,875
Maya...

266
00:15:02,958 --> 00:15:05,208
We're working on different
ways to transport you.

267
00:15:05,291 --> 00:15:06,875
Hopefully one will work out.

268
00:15:06,958 --> 00:15:08,250
Don't worry about it.

269
00:15:08,333 --> 00:15:11,250
I'd like to walk there
with my own two legs.

270
00:15:11,333 --> 00:15:13,875
Seri, Rina.
I guess this is it.

271
00:15:13,958 --> 00:15:14,625
Good-bye.

272
00:15:14,708 --> 00:15:15,875
No.

273
00:15:15,958 --> 00:15:17,875
Please let us stay with
you 'til the very end.

274
00:15:17,958 --> 00:15:20,750
We want to be there for you so
that we don't ever forget that

275
00:15:20,833 --> 00:15:22,541
the reason we were
able to survive

276
00:15:22,625 --> 00:15:25,041
was because of you, Tsubaki.

277
00:15:26,333 --> 00:15:28,333
I thank you.

278
00:15:29,500 --> 00:15:31,416
Kazuki!

279
00:15:32,250 --> 00:15:33,875
Why you!

280
00:15:46,958 --> 00:15:48,000
Those are pleiades-types!

281
00:15:48,083 --> 00:15:49,083
But they're so many!

282
00:15:49,166 --> 00:15:51,875
Everyone!
Tighten up the formation!

283
00:15:54,458 --> 00:15:57,458
Their leader has taken
the one o'clock position.

284
00:16:11,208 --> 00:16:15,000
Replace the units...
maintain efficiency.

285
00:16:15,083 --> 00:16:17,916
Lure in the source of
the enemy's power.

286
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:20,208
And then, destroy them all.

287
00:16:20,291 --> 00:16:23,541
That's right.
We will destroy all of them.

288
00:16:23,625 --> 00:16:25,333
And you will help us.

289
00:16:25,416 --> 00:16:29,958
With the minimum number of
sacrifices, destroy the enemy.

290
00:16:30,041 --> 00:16:32,208
Consider the amount
of sacrifices,

291
00:16:32,291 --> 00:16:34,625
but destroy the enemy.

292
00:16:36,458 --> 00:16:39,166
The enemy's
defensive line is retreating.

293
00:16:39,250 --> 00:16:40,666
What do you think that means?

294
00:16:40,750 --> 00:16:42,000
Could the Neo U.N.
be winning?

295
00:16:42,083 --> 00:16:43,083
No.

296
00:16:43,166 --> 00:16:44,833
Multiple enemy
units are alternating

297
00:16:44,916 --> 00:16:46,375
at the defensive front.

298
00:16:46,458 --> 00:16:49,000
This is a part of the Festums'
systematic fighting method.

299
00:16:49,083 --> 00:16:51,750
Before long, new units will
arrive and push us back.

300
00:16:51,833 --> 00:16:55,000
But since the Neo U.N.'s not
fighting cooperatively...

301
00:16:55,083 --> 00:16:57,333
They knew what they were getting
into from the beginning.

302
00:16:57,416 --> 00:16:58,750
Alright we'll take advantage of

303
00:16:58,833 --> 00:17:01,416
their retreat to
make our drop off.

304
00:17:01,500 --> 00:17:05,125
We have arrived at Point B.
Release the containers.

305
00:17:11,833 --> 00:17:13,083
Confirming their deployment.

306
00:17:13,166 --> 00:17:16,375
Let's get out of here!
We'll be back soon enough.

307
00:17:19,250 --> 00:17:21,500
There they are!
The new weapons!

308
00:17:22,500 --> 00:17:24,125
Good old Mr. Mizoguchi!

309
00:17:24,208 --> 00:17:26,625
It's exactly what we need.

310
00:17:44,250 --> 00:17:47,500
From here on,
we'll truly be on enemy turf.

311
00:17:48,333 --> 00:17:50,416
Let's do this!

312
00:18:01,041 --> 00:18:03,208
Look at them.
They're all headed that way.

313
00:18:03,291 --> 00:18:05,958
Do they not know that the
entrance is located over here?

314
00:18:06,041 --> 00:18:07,083
Guess not.

315
00:18:07,166 --> 00:18:08,333
And we have no way
of letting them know

316
00:18:08,416 --> 00:18:09,708
about the information we have.

317
00:18:09,791 --> 00:18:10,958
If we go forward,

318
00:18:11,041 --> 00:18:13,791
hopefully someone
will notice and follow us.

319
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:21,041
Here we go!

320
00:18:29,708 --> 00:18:31,791
What is this place?

321
00:18:37,500 --> 00:18:40,500
By fighting together,
we'll defeat them!

322
00:18:43,583 --> 00:18:47,458
The children of Alvis
have made it inside.

323
00:18:47,541 --> 00:18:51,791
What should we do?
How do we destroy them.

324
00:18:51,875 --> 00:18:54,000
Don't let them work together...

325
00:18:54,083 --> 00:18:57,291
Destroy... each one.

326
00:18:57,375 --> 00:18:59,416
Stop it!
No!

327
00:18:59,500 --> 00:19:01,458
Don't!
Not the wound.

328
00:19:01,541 --> 00:19:05,375
Tell us... how do we isolate
them from one another?

329
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:09,666
Pretend to be weak...
lure them in.

330
00:19:12,333 --> 00:19:16,166
You must make some
sacrifices... to do this.

331
00:19:16,250 --> 00:19:19,333
We understand and
will make it happen.

332
00:19:19,416 --> 00:19:22,166
We will use the hatred we've
learned from humans...

333
00:19:22,250 --> 00:19:25,250
...to destroy the
children of Alvis.

334
00:19:25,958 --> 00:19:27,291
W... wait...

335
00:19:30,750 --> 00:19:33,083
We've completed the work
of linking Valkyrie's Coagula

336
00:19:33,166 --> 00:19:34,500
to the rest of the system.

337
00:19:34,583 --> 00:19:38,041
We can begin the core's
re-synchronization at any time.

338
00:19:42,166 --> 00:19:45,708
The temporary connections
have checked out on all levels.

339
00:19:45,791 --> 00:19:49,625
Okay Tsubaki...
we're finally ready for you now.

340
00:20:00,625 --> 00:20:02,416
Tsubaki...

341
00:20:05,250 --> 00:20:07,375
To perform the core's
re-synchronization,

342
00:20:07,458 --> 00:20:09,791
we will be heading over
to the Valkyrie's Coagula.

343
00:20:09,875 --> 00:20:12,208
Tsubaki, what are those things?

344
00:20:12,291 --> 00:20:14,166
They are what connect
me to the coagula

345
00:20:14,250 --> 00:20:17,125
and assimilate me with
the rest of the island.

346
00:20:17,958 --> 00:20:19,208
If it's all right with you,

347
00:20:19,291 --> 00:20:21,291
would you please
let us hold them?

348
00:20:35,083 --> 00:20:35,833
Kenji!

349
00:20:35,916 --> 00:20:37,041
Canon!

350
00:20:46,375 --> 00:20:47,791
What?

351
00:20:49,375 --> 00:20:51,916
Kenji!
Canon!

352
00:20:56,416 --> 00:20:57,916
Kazuki!

353
00:21:04,625 --> 00:21:06,291
Everyone...

354
00:21:08,291 --> 00:21:10,750
Damn you!
Let go of me!

355
00:21:10,833 --> 00:21:12,708
Kenji!

356
00:21:42,916 --> 00:21:46,000
Hey guys!
Is anyone under attack?

357
00:21:46,416 --> 00:21:48,958
W-Where is everyone?

358
00:22:05,541 --> 00:22:06,375
Tch.

359
00:22:06,458 --> 00:22:08,500
I'm cut off from
the rest of 'em.

360
00:22:30,500 --> 00:22:32,875
The enemy's strengthening
their defensive line.

361
00:22:32,958 --> 00:22:34,583
The units in the area as well as

362
00:22:34,666 --> 00:22:36,750
incoming reinforcement
units are being cut off.

363
00:22:36,833 --> 00:22:39,333
Keep advancing.
Retreat is no longer an option!

364
00:22:39,416 --> 00:22:41,625
Full speed ahead!

365
00:22:46,416 --> 00:22:50,208
I'm making it back alive.
No matter what!

366
00:22:50,291 --> 00:22:52,291
Are you there?

367
00:22:52,750 --> 00:22:53,958
Before...

368
00:22:54,041 --> 00:22:56,375
I didn't exist
anywhere...

369
00:22:56,458 --> 00:23:00,041
But now it's different!
Because I am here!

370
00:23:05,625 --> 00:23:07,791
There is no way
I'm going to die!

371
00:23:07,875 --> 00:23:12,291
I won't die!
Do you hear me?

372
00:23:16,791 --> 00:23:19,708
Soon...
very soon...

373
00:23:19,791 --> 00:23:22,166
They will all understand.

374
00:23:22,250 --> 00:23:23,458
But until then...

375
00:23:23,541 --> 00:23:25,041
...they can...

376
00:23:25,125 --> 00:23:27,458
...stay alive.

377
00:23:35,291 --> 00:23:38,791
The cycle of existence
and nothingness.

378
00:23:39,833 --> 00:23:41,666
Pulling the trigger...

379
00:23:41,750 --> 00:23:44,125
...and choosing survival.

380
00:23:45,708 --> 00:23:46,916
I...

381
00:23:47,666 --> 00:23:50,500
I am going to disappear now...

382
00:23:51,875 --> 00:23:57,041
Next on Fafner...
the final episode.

383
00:23:57,125 --> 00:23:58,541
"The Sky."

384
00:23:59,250 --> 00:24:00,708
Are you there?

